  <description type="morphology">Plants erect, 3–6 dm, glabrous. Aerial flowering stems erect, 0.5–1 dm. Leaves basal or basal and cauline; blade oblong to oblong-ovate. Inflorescences 10–50 cm. Involucres sessile and appressed to branches, rarely on erect pedun-cles 1–5 mm at proximal nodes, cylindric, 3–3.5 mm. Flowers 1–1.5(–1.8) mm; perianth white. Achenes 1–1.4 mm.</description>
